            "id": 6519851,
            "title": "〈台股開盤〉逾千跌點回測4萬6後跌幅收斂 機器人、無人機聯歡齊嗨",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (2) 日受美股四大指數皆黑，科技股重挫影響，加上台積電 ADR 下殺 6.98% 影響，開盤 3 分鐘後受台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 下跌影響跌逾 1,037 點，一度跌破 46,000 大關，盤面上由強勢題材領軍，包括機器人、軍工無人機概念股各自表現，盤中在權值股回神下，跌幅收斂，暫報 46,670 點、跌 308 點或 0.6%，預估全日成交量縮減至 1.23 兆元。 </p></section><p><template id=\"P:1\"></template></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>權值股部分，台積電開盤跌 55 點或 2.2% 到 2,450，今日除息的鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 以貼息開出，下跌逾 1%；聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 跌 3.81%、台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 跌 3.2%)、智邦 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 漲逾 1.13%。傳產權值股部分，南亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>) 漲逾 2%、台化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1326:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1326\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1326-TW</a>) 漲 7%。</p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>盤面上，機器人概念股受惠於 Google 投資的人形機器人新創 Apptronik 宣布在德州推出機器人訓練設施「Robot Park」，加速人形機器人商業化，包括達明 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4585:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4585\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4585-TW</a>)、穎漢 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4562:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4562\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4562-TW</a>)、和椿 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6215:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6215\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6215-TW</a>)、泓格 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3577:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3577\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3577-TW</a>)、羅昇 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8374:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8374\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8374-TW</a>)、所羅門 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2359:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2359\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2359-TW</a>) 帶量齊嗨紛紛亮燈漲停。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>軍工無人機股則受惠在野黨分別公布無人機法案版本利多，包括力山 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1515:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1515\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1515-TW</a>) 飆漲停，雷虎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8033:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8033\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8033-TW</a>)、全訊 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:5222:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5222\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5222-TW</a>)、為升 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2231:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2231\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2231-TW</a>) 漲幅超過 3% 以上。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>法人表示，台股在短期均線上，大架構持續朝多方前進，惟受美股下跌拖累，短線走勢仍以震盪為主，盤面上以短多熱門標的為主，短線部分參考技術面操作因應。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美股今日凌晨收盤部分，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊</a>下跌 13.96 點或 0.03%，收報 52,305.24 點；標普 500 下跌 16.13 點或 0.22%，收 7,483.23 點；<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">那斯達克</a>下跌 173.69 點或 0.66%，收 26,040.03 點；費城重跌 893.68 點或 6.27%，收 13,353.28 點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p> </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6519851",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 10:20:39",
            "source": "cnyes",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
